            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">D(is) M(anibus)</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et memoriae Car<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/>t<supplied reason="lost">ull</supplied>i qui vixit an<lb break="no" n="3"/>nis XXXII Castus pa<lb break="no" n="4"/>ter et Castus Carat<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>lli <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> vivi <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>onendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Rechteckige Stele. Im bogenförmig abgeschlossenem Bildfeld Brustbilder einer Familie: Mann, Frau und Kind zwischen beiden. (B): Kleinere Abweichungen in Lesung/Ergänzung.</p>
            </div>
